  "title": "Several people saw a UFO moving like a windshield wiper in Senador Firmino [2003]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/several-people-saw-a-ufo-moving-like-a-windshield-wiper-in-senador-firmino-2003/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-iy",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 23rd, 2003</strong>. Time: 8:00 pm. Duration: 15 minutes. In the city of Senador Firmino, State of Minas Gerais, several people witnessed the sighting of an unidentified flying object &#8220;in the sky, making movement like a windshield wiper&#8221;, according to the words of the witness who provided information to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command ]. The UFO was round in shape and emitted a strong glow. Still according to the report, the visibility conditions at the time were &#8220;optimal&#8221;, &#8220;clear skies&#8221;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.635. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário com relato sobre avistamento de Ovni em Senador Firmino, Minas Gerais&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MAY 23rd, 2003. Time: 8:00 pm. Duration: 15 minutes. In the city of Senador Firmino, State of Minas Gerais, several people witnessed the sighting of an unidentified flying object &#8220;in the sky, making movement like a windshield wiper&#8221;, according to the words of the witness who provided information to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command ]. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
